Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,0:01:24.13,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Podľa novín
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.13,0:01:28.17,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}vzrástol počet automobilových nehôd detí nosiacich Okuliare.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.63,0:01:30.80,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej, vy tam! Prídete neskoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.03,0:01:33.30,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dobré ráno, Fumie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.48,0:01:36.14,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}D-dobré ráno!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.47,0:01:42.73,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nikdy by som si nepomyslela, že Sačči je Harakenovo zvieratko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:44.52,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nikdy nesúď knihu podľa obalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.09,0:01:47.52,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Na prvý pohľad na ňom nie je nič výnimočné.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.24,0:01:50.02,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je taký istý ako predtým.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:53.83,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pozrel sa sem!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:55.92,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Č-č-čo budeme robiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.14,0:01:55.92,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.02,0:01:59.31,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo tu robíte? Toto nie je vaša trieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.31,0:02:01.17,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}P-prepáč!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:04.80,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Všetci na miesta!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.80,0:02:06.70,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Na dnešnej hodine...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.46,0:02:09.13,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8}Nemá Sačči slúžiť ako automat mestu Daikoku?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:10.40,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Má.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:12.02,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je to tu napísané.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:14.04,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vyzerá to, ako by to napísal nejaký idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:16.96,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hlavne to meno... Sačči...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.42,0:02:21.29,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jeho hlúpe správanie sa nedá nazvať „upratovaním“.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:22.55,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Presne tak!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:25.37,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kvôli najmenšiemu metabugu sa správa ako šialený.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:27.73,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stavím sa, že ten, kto ho programoval bol nejaký hyster...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:28.64,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej, vy dve!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:31.94,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tu sa bavíme o dôležitých veciach, tak dávajte pozor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:37.46,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}V poslednej dobe sa tu objavil úchyl napádajúci malé deti.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:39.34,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čoskoro začnú letné prázdniny,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:40.86,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}preto buďte opatrní a nebavte sa s cudzími ľuďmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.07,0:02:44.61,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ahoj!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:48.83,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A dávajte si pozor na podozrivých ľudí.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:55.13,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Služobník zla?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:58.40,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haraken iba predstiera, že nič nevie,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:01.59,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ale v skutočnosti je to služobník zla.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.59,0:03:04.17,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aj tak sa mi nechce veriť, že Sačči je jeho zvieratko...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:06.66,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To môžeš povedať len preto, lebo si to nevidela.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:10.61,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vieš, že mňa okuliare veľmi nebavia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:14.47,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prečo vlastne Haraken začal skúmať Ilegálov?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:16.55,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ktovie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.37,0:03:19.54,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ach, už viem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.54,0:03:21.54,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Požiadalo ho o to jedno dievča.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:24.05,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ale to dievča...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:25.85,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Presne tak, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.13,0:03:28.02,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.82,0:03:29.67,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To dievča
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:30.69,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}zomrelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:33.03,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}IStalo sa to pred rokom cez letné prázdniny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:34.81,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čože? Ona zomrela?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.12,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vraj ju zrazilo auto pri križovatke Nakacu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:40.32,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aj mňa to šokovalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.91,0:03:43.15,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oni dvaja začali s výskumom,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:45.48,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ale iba jeden ho dokončil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:47.17,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Volala sa Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:50.33,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bola to Harakenova susedka a kamarátka z detstva.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:53.59,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ale on vyzeral, ako by ho to vôbec nešokovalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:55.34,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Len odvtedy chodí ako námesačný.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:56.86,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Možno máš pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:04:00.34,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haraken nie je typ, čo by ukazoval navonok svoje city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:02.90,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Možno to bola preňho veľká rana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:06.49,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No to nič nemení na fakte,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:08.99,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}že je to služobník zla!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:09.80,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jasako,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:12.74,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}cez prestávku pokračujeme v našom pláne!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.74,0:04:14.70,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Naozaj sa chceš do toho pustiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:16.35,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ja neviem...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:20.26,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kde si?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:22.36,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prečo si ma sem zavolala?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:23.12,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ani hnúť!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.38,0:04:26.32,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ruky hore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:28.07,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}O niečo sa pokús
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:29.17,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}a strelím!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:30.43,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:33.84,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ako si sa dostal k Saččimu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:35.05,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hovor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:36.58,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prestaňte...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:38.96,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Odhalili sme ťa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:39.88,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Priznaj sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:44.08,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}N...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:44.97,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}N...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:47.59,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nemôžem vám to prezradiť, lebo je to tajné!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:52.97,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tajné?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:53.92,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tu je to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:55.09,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sľub mlčanlivosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.09,0:04:59.22,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Povinnosť dodržiavať klientove záujmy a neposkytovať informácie bez jeho súhlasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:02.21,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dosť dobre tomu nerozumiem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:05.02,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aby som bola úprimná, Harakenovi nerozumiem vôbec.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.02,0:05:08.34,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Keď sme sa prvýkrát stretli, nebývall taký zachmúrený.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:12.70,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ako dlho sa poznáte?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:13.65,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:17.24,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Po prvýkrát sme sa stretli minulý rok kvôli jeho výskumu Ilegálov.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:19.35,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nespomínam si presne
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:21.16,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kedy vstúpil do nášho klubu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:22.70,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A čo jeho rodina?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:26.93,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jeho otec pracuje pre firmu na výrobu kyberzvieratiek.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:28.41,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ale Haraken toho veľa o sebe neprezradí.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.92,0:05:31.23,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}O sebe skoro vôbec nehovorí.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:33.33,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tam je!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:47.20,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nemám z nej dobrý pocit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:49.04,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Už viem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:50.18,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:53.11,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Naša učka spomínala, že sa tu potuluje niekto, kto číha na deti.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:55.47,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prestaň! Desíš ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:56.81,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kde je Haraken?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:58.19,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A jejda!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.56,0:06:04.78,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nevedela som, že má také dospelácke záujmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:06.90,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je správanie je nevypočítateľné!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.35,0:06:11.80,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo myslíš, že je to „obchodné tajomstvo“?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:13.70,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Keď o tom hovoríš,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:15.44,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}spomínal niečo, čo ma zmiatlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:17.90,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Niečo o zvieratku jeho tety, alebo tak nejako.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:19.29,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Už si spomínam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.76,0:06:23.63,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takže jeho teta má na starosti Saččiho.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:30.03,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To sa k Saččimu nehodí.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:31.55,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pozri!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:34.89,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Teta?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:37.65,Coil Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oba-san (teta) používa sa aj ako označenie staršej ženy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:37.65,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A nosí okuliare.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:39.75,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Podozrivé.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:42.03,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fumie, pozri!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:47.73,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Niet pochýb!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:49.57,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To kvetinárstvo je iba zásterka!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:52.08,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}V skutočnosti je to Saččiho skrýša!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:55.23,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A tá milo vyzerajúca pani je...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:06:56.58,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...nepriateľ všetkých detí!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:59.07,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Saččiho šéfka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:05.88,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nakoniec sa nám Haraken stratil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:09.22,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ako o ňom môžeme získať nejaké informácie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:10.87,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1Už viem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.87,0:07:11.52,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:12.77,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Megaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:14.61,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je predsa piatym členom klubu, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.61,0:07:16.39,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Určite vie toho o Harakenovi veľa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:17.55,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Máš pravdu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:18.46,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Úplne som na to zabudla!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:20.44,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Veď som ti hovorila.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:22.34,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Babička odišla k horúcim prameňom v Jugaware.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.95,0:07:24.13,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Úplne som zabudla.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:25.34,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zavolajme jej.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:29.93,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je raj.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:35.03,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Som taká rada, že máme horúce pramene priamo uprostred mesta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:36.10,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Veru tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:39.32,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mimochodom, ako sa to voláš?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:43.64,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tome, už som ti povedala, že som Okonogi z hračkárstva.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:46.36,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Už viem, už viem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:49.01,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mimochodom...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:51.37,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prečo nosíš okuliare aj počas kúpania?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:54.87,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pokiaľ sa nenamočia, je to v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:57.29,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je raj.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:07:59.29,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Veru tak, raj.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:04.46,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mimochodom, ako sa to voláš?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:10.41,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Skvelé, konečne som sa ti dovolala.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:14.76,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To si ty, Osmička Jasako?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:15.64,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:18.75,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vlastne som sa ťa chcela na niečo spýtať.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:20.16,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ide o Päťku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:21.74,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vydrž chvíľu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.65,0:08:24.71,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo si hovorila, Tome?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:29.41,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pýtala som sa, či je v poriadku nosiť okuliare počas kúpania.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:31.98,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pokiaľ sa nenamočia, je to v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:37.10,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haló? Haló?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:38.88,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zložila to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:40.53,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nevychovaná vnučka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:44.83,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Naša jediná stopa práve zložila.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:46.87,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takže musíme pokračovať vo vyšetrovaní na vlastnú päsť.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:48.87,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Poďte sa hrať!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:50.41,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Daj už pokoj.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:52.07,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Toto je nebezpečné.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:52.96,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Protiva!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:55.93,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Má iba jeden sandál!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.84,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je taká nepozorná.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:01.37,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Niečo nové?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:03.04,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nič nové tu nie je.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:05.55,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}V tom prípade som na rade ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:06.28,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:08.38,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ako podpredsedníčka Biologického krúžku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:08.89,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pozri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:11.18,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:13.68,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Toto som našla v klubovni.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:16.27,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pozrieme sa na Saččiho z biologického hľadiska.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:22.63,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ja Sačči!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:23.73,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Teší ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:26.43,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Obyčajne útočí na kurobugy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:28.81,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kurobugy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:30.13,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pokračujme.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:33.82,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Obyčajne útočí aj na metabugy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:35.85,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Metabugy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:36.33,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ďalej.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:40.34,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ďalší zvyčajný cieľ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:42.47,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Metatagy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:42.92,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ďalej.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.96,0:09:48.22,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Skoro všetko, čo Megaba vytvorila je ilegálne.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:50.13,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Udica...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.83,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, to sa dalo čakať.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:52.42,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ďalej.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:55.22,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hovienko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:58.24,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ja Sačči!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:00.09,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tadeto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.42,0:10:03.50,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo to dopekla stváraš?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:04.73,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je to nebezpečné!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:06.75,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ja sa chcem s vami hrať!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:07.95,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Densuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:09.98,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Teraz zostáva zistiť, aký má dostrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:19.19,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dokáže rozoznať cieľ na desať metrov.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:20.49,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Desať metrov...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:28.09,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dokáže rozoznať cieľ na dvadsať metrov.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:29.75,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dvadsať metrov...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.28,0:10:35.03,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zdá sa, že z tridsiatich metrov ho nevidí.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.81,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pozorovanie je veľmi dôležité.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:43.09,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ale na pomoc pri hliadkovaní majú Kjú-čan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:43.96,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takže...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:47.36,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dozvedeli sme sa toho veľa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:48.76,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kjóko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:50.34,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hovienko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:54.93,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uteč!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.61,0:11:00.39,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stoj!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:08.10,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.97,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nepribližuj sa k nám!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:15.88,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tu máš.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:26.50,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hovorila som ti, že je to nebezpečné!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:29.01,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nesmieš ma len tak prenasledovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:32.74,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Keď tu ešte nebol Sačči, bola to omnoho väčšia zábava.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:35.15,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fumie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:37.81,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nemyslíš, že si bola k Harakenovi nespravodlivá?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:43.54,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pred mesiacom mi Sačči zabil zvieratko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:47.80,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bola to kybermyška, ktorú som chovala tri roky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:49.45,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mala iba malý bug...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.94,0:11:51.62,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vysvetľovanie bolo zbytočné...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:53.05,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A preto ju zabil?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:54.73,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Už nikdy nechcem mať zvieratko,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:56.58,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}pretože to bolí, keď zomrú...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:58.44,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aj keď nie sú skutočné.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:00.36,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A čo Ujo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.99,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hovorila som ti, že je to sluha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:05.02,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nie je to zvieratko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.02,0:12:06.43,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tu máš, Kjóko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:07.49,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vyznačila som ti cestu domov.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:10.00,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nevedela som, že je po ceste toľko svätýň.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:13.58,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Svätyne nie sú jediné miesto, kam Sačči nemôže vstúpiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:16.75,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sú to aj parky, školy a očividne aj nemocnice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:20.32,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prečo tam Sačči nemôže vstúpiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:22.25,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kvôli prísnej hierarchii.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:24.74,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sačči patrí pod Ministerstvo pôšt,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:26.29,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}preto nemôže vstúpiť do oblastí pod správou iných ministerstiev.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:30.28,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Napríklad nemôže vstúpiť do miest pod správou Ministerstva školstva alebo kultúry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.62,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Svätyne patria pod Ministerstvo kultúry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:33.50,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:37.89,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takisto vnútro domu je označené ako „vnútorná oblasť“.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:40.62,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}a je odlišné od „vonkajšej oblasti“, ktorá sa nachádza na ulici.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.62,0:12:42.36,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Preto nemôžu vstúpiť do domu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:45.75,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Choď domov podľa presne podľa mapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:49.98,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ak neposlúchneš, zlý Sačči si ťa nájde!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:52.58,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hovienko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:59.10,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:24.56,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nechce sa mi veriť, že tá teta
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:26.43,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}je vlastne agentkou Ministerstva pôšt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:28.02,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Predsa si to videla!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:30.23,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sačči vyšiel z tej steny!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:33.61,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ale ak sa mýlime, máme problém.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:35.11,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hotovo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:36.56,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Naozaj to bude v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.34,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nezabokovala som všetko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:41.14,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ale prečo to mám byť ja a nie ty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:45.45,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mám príliš veľa vecí na to, aby som ich zablokovala.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:47.49,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Neboj sa, budeš úplne v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:50.50,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ale ak sa mi pokazia okuliare, zaplatíš za opravu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:04.51,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bude to v poriadku...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:09.37,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nebude!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:12.70,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nebude!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:23.31,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nie je to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.31,0:14:24.36,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...to dievča?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:28.71,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je zvláštne.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:31.34,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sken nenašiel u teba žiadne bugy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:32.54,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No tak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:34.22,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stálo ma to skoro dvojročné vreckové!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:35.52,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je divné...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:38.97,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jasako, nechytila si nejaký zlý bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:39.75,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8}No dovoľ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.23,0:14:42.74,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mimochodom, Fumie...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:44.71,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Práve ma niečo napadlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:45.34,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:48.23,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nepomohlo by vypnúť okuliare?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.82,0:14:58.57,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Už je to rok, čo som naposledy vypla okuliare.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:15:00.60,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cítim sa bez nich divne.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:03.33,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je v nich zabudovaný aj mobil,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:05.46,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}preto ich zriedkakedy vypínam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:09.52,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Možno už je neskoro na to byť normálnymi deťmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:11.67,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vitajte.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.73,0:15:13.43,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Áno?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:15.75,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}S-ste...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:16.39,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Áno?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:19.23,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ste agentkou Ministerstva pôšt?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:21.34,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Chcela tým povedať,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:22.99,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ste Harakenova teta?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:24.62,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Harakawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:28.25,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ach, vy musíte byť Kenove kamarátky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:29.11,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:30.80,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Chcete vedieť, či sme príbuzní?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:32.46,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vôbec nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:35.36,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Poznám ho už odmalička.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:39.49,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Volá vás Haraken teta?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:43.21,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ken ma vždy volá pani kvetinárka.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:45.94,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prečo vás to zaujíma?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:46.99,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takže vy nie ste...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:48.65,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prepáčte, že sme obťažovali.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:50.98,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Počkajte...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:55.77,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ken sa po tej nehode prestal usmievať.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:15:58.68,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Skúste ho trocha rozveseliť.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.35,0:16:09.98,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tak tu si.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:14.38,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Minulý rok, počas nášho výskumu,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:16.12,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}som sa s Kannou pohádal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:18.97,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kanna bola nahnevaná,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:20.14,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}lebo som to nebral vážne.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:23.70,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Odišla s tým, že ide k tejto križovatke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:25.67,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Už nikdy sa nevrátila.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:27.19,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haraken...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:32.11,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kannu pravdepodobne zabil Ilegál.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:36.37,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vedeli ste, že moderný dopravný systém
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:38.90,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}je napojený na kyberpriestor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:42.07,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej, kybernavi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:43.78,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zdá, že auto, čo zabilo Kannu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:47.57,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}bolo ovládané kybernavi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:48.39,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čože?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:53.08,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ale nemal by autopilot byť stopercentne bezpečný?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:55.21,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Moja teta si myslí,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:57.88,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}že príčinou chýb v kybernavi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:16:59.83,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}môžu byť Ilegálovia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:01.39,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tak preto skúmaš Ilegálov...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:04.10,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kto je tvoja teta?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:06.58,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je to tiež tajné?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:09.53,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je to otcova mladšia sestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:10.29,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Moja teta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:14.65,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pracuje v oddelení manažmentu Daikockého kyberpriestoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:15.62,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Naozaj?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.15,0:17:18.57,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To moja teta naprogramovala Saččiho.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:22.69,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Keď som jej povedal, že chcem pokračovať vo výskume Ilegálov,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:25.00,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}umožnila mi zastaviť Saččiho presne na jednu minútu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:28.68,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ale jediné povely, ktoré môžem použiť,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:31.31,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}sú „stoj“, “sadni“ a „podaj pac“.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:32.81,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tak je to teda...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:36.53,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nakoniec bol prípad uzavretý s tým,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:41.11,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}a preto chyba autopilota nie je pripisovaná za vinu vodičovi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.81,0:17:43.07,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nakoniec bol prípad uzavretý s tým,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:46.59,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}že to zapríčinila Kannina nepozornosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:52.02,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Budem pokračovať vo výskume aj tento rok.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:55.18,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nikto iný to nespraví.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:56.82,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Lebo inak,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:17:58.83,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kanna nebude odpočívať v pokoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:02.44,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haraken...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:04.68,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prepáč, že som ťa nazvala služobníkom zla.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:07.19,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pomôžem ti s výskumom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:08.55,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aj ja!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.55,0:18:09.96,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sme predsa v tom istom klube!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:12.55,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:17.65,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.48,0:18:19.24,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kjóko?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.89,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Poslala som ju domov už pred hodinou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:24.49,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stalo sa niečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:26.10,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ešte neprišla domov?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:28.54,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vedela som to! Mala som ju odviesť domov!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:30.85,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kjóko... myslíš to dievča, čo bolo s tebou predtým?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:32.37,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:34.75,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Videl som ju pred chvíľou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:36.11,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pri križovatke Nakacu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:37.91,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Našla si ju?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:38.84,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:39.96,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A vy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:40.72,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:43.05,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prečo nemôžeme použiť mapu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:44.42,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jej mobil je mimo dosahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:47.45,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}V tejto oblasti je slabý signál.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:49.54,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Toto je druhé najhoršie miesto v Daikoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:51.02,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A čo postranné uličky?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.73,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ulice sú tu ako bludisko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:55.50,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rozdelíme sa a pohľadáme ju!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:18:59.68,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kjóko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:08.51,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kjóko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:10.58,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo teraz?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:12.36,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Som zlá sestra...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:16.26,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sačči...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:18.29,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Densuke je v nebezpečenstve!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:19.19,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Musím ju rýchlo nájsť!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:22.70,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kjóko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.81,0:19:44.46,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kjóko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:53.42,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kjóko, si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:58.55,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Poznáš týchto dvoch?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:19:59.70,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{Uh?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:01.45,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Áno, toto je moja mladšia sestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:04.00,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Táto oblasť je nebezpečná. Dávajte si pozor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:06.06,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kedysi sa tu stala nehoda.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:08.10,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Áno... ja viem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:10.37,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Veľmi pekne vám ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:11.59,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jasako!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:13.18,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kjóko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:14.28,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vďakabohu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:16.07,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je ten úchyl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.77,0:20:23.72,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sačči!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.77,0:20:23.72,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sačči!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:24.76,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stoj!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.51,0:20:28.26,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Podaj pac!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:30.61,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sadni!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:35.25,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kto ste?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.01,0:20:39.85,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hráte sa s nebezpečnými hračkami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:42.88,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}N-neviem, o čom to hovoríte.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:44.18,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Viete...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:46.07,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Celkom dobre sa vyznám v hackovaní.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:47.26,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}V metatagoch a podobne.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:50.18,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kto vlastne ste?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:51.54,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tak ste ju našli!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:52.43,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vďakabohu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:54.10,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:55.77,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Teta!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:58.01,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Teta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:58.01,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Teta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:00.69,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No tak, Ken...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:02.77,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hovorila som ti, aby si ma nevolal teta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:06.21,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Som predsa živá 17-ročná mladica.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:09.17,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mladica?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:10.38,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Také zastarané slovo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.38,0:21:11.67,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Predstavím vás.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:13.00,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jasako, Fumie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.51,0:21:14.96,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Moja teta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:16.85,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:19.27,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hovorila som ti, aby si sa vyhýbal zlej spoločnosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:21.30,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ony nie sú zlé!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:23.58,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pomáhajú mi s výskumom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:25.58,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je jedno.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.19,0:21:28.71,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tentokrát prižmúrim oko, tak sa straťte.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:30.59,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ken, ideme domov.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.53,0:21:39.74,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ocko, ešte nevychádzaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.74,0:21:41.63,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dobre, dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:43.85,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Som po dnešku taká unavená,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:45.18,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}že vôbec netuším, čo bude ďalej.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.93,0:21:48.44,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ja som tiež unavený z práce.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.19,0:21:51.99,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tvoja únava s mojou nemá vôbec nič spoločné!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.44,0:21:54.23,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prečo si na mňa odrazu taká zlá?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.23,0:21:56.94,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Modlím sa, aby všetci dospelí protivní na svoje deti zmizli.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.86,0:22:02.20,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vôbec nerozumiem ženám.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.53,0:22:05.31,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prečo to tak veľmi potrebujete?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:07.99,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ak na to mám minúť toľko peňazí daňových poplatníkov
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.62,0:22:10.04,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}chcem aspoň nejaké vysvetlenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.10,0:22:13.59,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Keď hovorím, že je to nevyhnutné, tak je to nevyhnutné.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.77,0:22:19.50,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ako konzultantka kyberpriestorového manažmentu mám na to právomoc!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.30,0:22:17.28,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ako konzultantka kyberpriestorového manažmentu mám na to právomoc!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:22.70,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ak sa nemýlim, pán riaditeľ, len nedávno ste sem prestúpili z Kanazawy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:25.97,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nezabudnite na tú žiadosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.51,0:22:31.81,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vôbec nerozumiem ženám.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.73,0:22:36.89,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dokončili ste tie úpravy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.89,0:22:37.47,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:41.29,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Naozaj potrebujeme taký silný automat?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:42.81,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Potrebujeme ho tak veľmi, že jeden nestačí.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.48,0:22:45.66,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pochopíš to neskôr.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.28,0:22:49.72,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Včera to bolo ťažké.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:50.55,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:52.79,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ty si sa sem prisťahovala?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.79,0:22:53.88,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.88,0:22:56.08,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dohodnime sa, ako si rozdelíme prácu na výskume.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:57.24,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.99,0:22:59.58,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čo je s tebou, Jasako?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.58,0:23:01.21,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Viem, že si unavená, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.21,0:23:02.97,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je to kvôli tomu, čo sa stalo včera?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.49,0:23:06.37,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nie je to kvôli tomu...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.37,0:23:07.23,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tak kvôli čomu?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.29,0:23:13.88,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je taká už od rána.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:15.31,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je to...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:16.16,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...to čo si myslím...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:19.65,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Myslím, že začala obdivovať Harakenovu tetu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.11,0:23:21.66,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je to jej nová zábavka.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.66,0:23:24.53,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.54,0:24:50.80,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nabudúce v Dennou Coil:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.32,0:24:53.63,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Z cesty! Detektívna agentúra Coil.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.21,0:24:56.01,Coil Override,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tešte sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Coil Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{isako you're so cool!}
